-- China Will Be World's Largest Wind Power Market by 2030, Greenpeace Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-12T04:38:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/china-will-be-world-s-largest-wind-power-market-by-2030-greenpeace-says.html
China will be the world’s largest
single wind power market by 2030, Sven Teske, director of
Greenpeace International’s renewable energy campaign, said at a
briefing in Beijing today.  One in three wind power turbines erected in 2010 was in
China, Teske said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
